post.description:
**Detect language** of subtitle file.

At least 1 credits on user account is needed. [Buy Credits](../open_api.json/paths/~1ai~1credits~1buy/get)

Method is returning 
```
{
  "data": {
    "format": "SubRip",
    "type": "text",
    "language": {
      "W3C": "en",
      "name": "english",
      "native": "english",
      "ISO_639_1": "en",
      "ISO_639_2b": "eng"
    }
  }
}
```
